OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome breaks
OL,6,Fin the cloud possible giving a
OL,7,Fbrighter end to the day, scattered
OL,8,Fshowers slowly dying out later. Clear
OL,9,Fskies overnight allowing for a chilly
OL,10,Fnight. Blustery winds gradually easing
OL,11,Fthrough the evening, remaining lighter
OL,12,Fovernight.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FChilly start to Saturday
OL,15,Fwith cloud increasing from the
OL,16,Fsouthwest, some patchy rain possible,
OL,17,Fpotentially heavy later. Turning
OL,18,Fincreasingly windy as Storm Dave
OL,19,Farrives with gales and severe gales
OL,20,Fdeveloping.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
